			"styles": "\n\t/* bare :is() (no element prefix) — 100 chars exactly, stays inline (boundary) */\n\t:is(.aaaaaa, .bbbbbb, .cccccc, .dddddd, .eeeeee, .ffffff, .gggggg, .hhhhhh, .iiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiii) {\n\t\tcolor: red;\n\t}\n\t/* bare :is() — 101 chars, wraps one-per-line (exceeds print_width) */\n\t:is(\n\t\t.aaaaaa,\n\t\t.bbbbbb,\n\t\t.cccccc,\n\t\t.dddddd,\n\t\t.eeeeee,\n\t\t.ffffff,\n\t\t.gggggg,\n\t\t.hhhhhh,\n\t\t.iiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiii\n\t) {\n\t\tcolor: blue;\n\t}\n",
